text: Agrapidochori is a settlement in the West side of Elis, Peloponnese, Greece. Nativity of Mary Orthodox Church can be found in Agrapidochori settlement. ==See also== *List of settlements in Elis ==References== ==External links== * Page of Agrapidochori settlement in Elis Category:Populated places in Elis
